dismissalText.commentary: Paul Collingwood run out (Singh/Dhoni) 47 (55b 7x4 0x6 80m) SR: 85.45

dismissalComment.html: India have effected a run-out. Even Robin Singh must be pleasantly surprised. That's a huge wicket too. Collingwood is gone. It was tossed-up, outside off stump and Bopara pushed to point. Bopara didn't want the run, Collingwood wanted it and he pressed on. But Bopara's hesitation slowed him down a touch , RP Singh swooped on the ball and fired in a throw to Dhoni who whipped the bails off, with Collingwood out of his crease. It was refered upstairs and verdict was out.

commentTextItems.html: That's it. England have won. Full in length, on the middle and leg,d riven towards mid-on and they rush across.  England lead 3-1 in the series. It has been a wonderful partnership between Bopara and Broad. Cool, calm and skillful.

commentPostTextItems.html: Bopara and Broad came together when England were tottering at 114 for 7 and have stitched a memorable 99-run partnership to take England home. Broad's all-round brilliance has earned him the Man-of-the-Match award. An awesome effort, really. Thats all we have for you tonight, folks. Do join us for the fifth match live from Headingley on Sunday, September 2. This is Sriram Veera signing off. Cheers!

dismissalText.commentary: Paul Collingwood run out (Singh/Dhoni) 47 (55b 7x4 0x6 80m) SR: 85.45

dismissalComment.html: India have effected a run-out. Even Robin Singh must be pleasantly surprised. That's a huge wicket too. Collingwood is gone. It was tossed-up, outside off stump and Bopara pushed to point. Bopara didn't want the run, Collingwood wanted it and he pressed on. But Bopara's hesitation slowed him down a touch , RP Singh swooped on the ball and fired in a throw to Dhoni who whipped the bails off, with Collingwood out of his crease. It was refered upstairs and verdict was out.
